{"tid":188480,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土設計】港鐵poster","createTime":"2017-04-05T16:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T10:41:46.000Z","uid":16485,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3dc244a5414ca2e79c353cbf1d06b26e77aeb7a","tid":188480,"uid":16485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:45:38.000Z","msg":"哈囉各位巴絲打，小弟呢排整咗張港鐵poster。<br />\n<br />\n雖然港鐵年年加價， 服務又有待改善，但始終對於我哋香港人來講係一個無可取代嘅集體回憶。希望作為香港人嘅您可以支持一下呢個Project，無論係一個小小嘅Pledge，又或者係一個小小嘅分享，小弟都萬分感激。<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Y6zU7E0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FY6zU7E0.jpg&h=e196d282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/dadudeterry/the-hong-kong-mtr-poster-reborn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fdadudeterry%2Fthe-hong-kong-mtr-poster-reborn&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=cc2a86f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/dadudeterry/the-hong-kong-mtr-poster-reborn</a>"},{"pid":"b942d072e9147145e8202a733db70e5f68bbb56d","tid":188480,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:08:26.000Z","msg":"a few stations added?"},{"pid":"77d9a0d59bc8f848a59743cc8a043df5f9d24f78","tid":188480,"uid":53082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:13:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"608478339ef4e01547aae1874bb3e8da733bd5c5","tid":188480,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T19:36:47.000Z","msg":"仲想話見過個類似project，原來你之前都出過mtr poster <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5d85cec60e0ec8469bca2957ef944c8439975a","tid":188480,"uid":16485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:12:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲想話見過個類似project，原來你之前都出過mtr poster <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 但係麻麻地滿意上次出嚟果個成品 所以再做多次"},{"pid":"3a2022bd767c45816ef739cb6e4c0f97229db299","tid":188480,"uid":16485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>a few stations added?</blockquote><br />\n要唔要搵地方寄賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5181 8232</blockquote><br />\n暫時未有貨呀 因為我係學生冇乜錢一嘢揼落去 所以先要攪眾籌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eef7e1d55dd2532dd1bc0a906c7f123d9074d1e","tid":188480,"uid":16485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>a few stations added?</blockquote><br />\n加咗新個幾條線"},{"pid":"855ee2e492773ba641204913df66aa9ad6d6b14b","tid":188480,"uid":21278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:43:01.000Z","msg":"唔知有咩用 但正評左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e65220f2a8400a48576aabea1e99152a19ad1e","tid":188480,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:05:36.000Z","msg":"港鐵對車站字體及配色有版權，標誌更不在話下（註冊商標）。<br />\n所以推出海報前，宜先詢問法律意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cadf656345fb58cdaee049b21ef7e5af8ce0be3","tid":188480,"uid":26161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:21:25.000Z","msg":"幾靚"},{"pid":"649f9b26aea67f39af00e0f515b0bc4063b19a9b","tid":188480,"uid":16485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T23:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港鐵對車站字體及配色有版權，標誌更不在話下（註冊商標）。<br />\n所以推出海報前，宜先詢問法律意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n地鐵用嘅中文字體叫做 MTRsong 而佢喺為地鐵度身訂造嘅。係網上面好難搵到，而就算搵到，作為一個學生，我根本負擔唔起。再者，用相關字體亦有可能侵犯地鐵嘅財產。為咗盡量保存MTRsong 嘅aesthetics, 我用咗華儷中宋(which MTRsong is based on)。喺呢度希望大家見諒。"},{"pid":"6908b941c1ee0f2fce57cc9014678d8bd0950da4","tid":188480,"uid":47823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:56:17.000Z","msg":"油麻地應該用紅白藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d5efd1748a3b59421e057bcf2aa2283135787e","tid":188480,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:59:21.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下有咩特別"},{"pid":"45d3a3abc7e262c53173032f022133b3589cf63a","tid":188480,"uid":16485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以講下有咩特別</blockquote><br />\n個concept係根據唔同車站嘅顏色，順序排列，一來睇落美觀啲, 以來擺係客廳或者房裡面都唔會話好唔合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095766e581f8883b211ddd9e0ed9eb590b43febf","tid":188480,"uid":16485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以講下有咩特別</blockquote><br />\n個concept係根據唔同車站嘅顏色，順序排列，一來睇落美觀啲, 二來擺係客廳或者房裡面都唔會話好唔合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"315234b7ba7fe553d278aa6946e5cbecb326bb08","tid":188480,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:16:55.000Z","msg":"老老實實, 唔係潑冷水<br />\n但張poster 只係copy &amp; paste <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851b779edb3af03dffe3600a40150bb64c495a11","tid":188480,"uid":44783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:20:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以講下有咩特別</blockquote><br />\n個concept係根據唔同車站嘅顏色，順序排列，一來睇落美觀啲, 以來擺係客廳或者房裡面都唔會話好唔合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寫哂D 車站出黎又有咩特別?"},{"pid":"4247812b85e2ece7d7032ac189f32f701cf633f8","tid":188480,"uid":33429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:22:15.000Z","msg":"邊個會係自己地方貼d咁既野?"},{"pid":"2bc119f7394779cf15adbad17193b9beaa03b0c9","tid":188480,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:21:01.000Z","msg":"老老實實, 係街派我都唔會貼係屋企...<br />\n<br />\n毫無美觀, 試下將創意放係第二到, 加油"},{"pid":"4cbc0a54aaa06d70ea4677ef77e55a575de13222","tid":188480,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:56:52.000Z","msg":"You should understand your target audience, key message<br />\nIf u are art for art's sake, u are having art, not design."},{"pid":"656bc22956a3ac3b90c8e2cee9d39430d20612f9","tid":188480,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以講下有咩特別</blockquote><br />\n個concept係根據唔同車站嘅顏色，順序排列，一來睇落美觀啲, 以來擺係客廳或者房裡面都唔會話好唔合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋呢個只係佢個form嘅特點 concept係你點解要做 想向咩人表達啲乜 作為觀眾嘅我地 又可唔可以get到你想表達嘅野"},{"pid":"b22b5e9791b686bd3e9a1839e2fcb616b893eb07","tid":188480,"uid":16485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以講下有咩特別</blockquote><br />\n個concept係根據唔同車站嘅顏色，順序排列，一來睇落美觀啲, 以來擺係客廳或者房裡面都唔會話好唔合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋呢個只係佢個form嘅特點 concept係你點解要做 想向咩人表達啲乜 作為觀眾嘅我地 又可唔可以get到你想表達嘅野</blockquote><br />\n可能我答下點解會做呢張Poster先啦。最主要係因為小弟自己係外國讀書；而係外國讀書嘅我好想推廣香港人呢個Identity（因為好多鬼佬真係唔知／唔識／唔會留意／覺得同大陸一樣）。咁就諗，不如索性整張港鐵嘅Poster，等啲唔熟悉香港嘅朋友可以認識一下香港；而當我個FLAT搞house party／pre-drinks個陣，亦都係一個好好嘅convo starter。<br />\n<br />\n以至於Audience wise, 就呢度嘅Feedback嚟睇，可能係香港住嘅香港人未必對我呢個project有興趣啦，始終日日都見到唔會覺得有咩特別，但係對於旅居海外嘅香港人來講，叫做有啲嘢可以懷緬下。"},{"pid":"8e3ffa3cbb19529c5ce9c9c2ef96c6945805101f","tid":188480,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以講下有咩特別</blockquote><br />\n個concept係根據唔同車站嘅顏色，順序排列，一來睇落美觀啲, 以來擺係客廳或者房裡面都唔會話好唔合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋呢個只係佢個form嘅特點 concept係你點解要做 想向咩人表達啲乜 作為觀眾嘅我地 又可唔可以get到你想表達嘅野</blockquote><br />\n可能我答下點解會做呢張Poster先啦。最主要係因為小弟自己係外國讀書；而係外國讀書嘅我好想推廣香港人呢個Identity（因為好多鬼佬真係唔知／唔識／唔會留意／覺得同大陸一樣）。咁就諗，不如索性整張港鐵嘅Poster，等啲唔熟悉香港嘅朋友可以認識一下香港；而當我個FLAT搞house party／pre，-drinks個陣，亦都係一個好好嘅convo starter。<br />\n<br />\n以至於Audience wise, 就呢度嘅Feedback嚟睇，可能係香港住嘅香港人未必對我呢個project有興趣啦，始終日日都見到唔會覺得有咩特別，但係對於旅居海外嘅香港人來講，叫做有啲嘢可以懷緬下。</blockquote><br />\n我覺得個target audience要分得好啲 你一時話係foreigner 一時話係海外香港人 好老實講 係好難同時滿足到呢兩種target audience"},{"pid":"353f7a2d5e937de9ca7f14e8b66c49ff47787f68","tid":188480,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:12:26.000Z","msg":"因為呢個都屬於collective memory <br />\n咁你比啲洋鬼子睇 佢地咪純粹知「oh nigga it's the station names! Fuck up dude」好難去令佢地了解香港人嘅identity <br />\n反而比overseas hkers 作為一個思鄉嘅物品 係無乜題 但會考慮嘅係 呢四年新加嘅站其實係可以唔要"},{"pid":"fdcd911934bc77796e299b3b1e363a547b57ca16","tid":188480,"uid":54627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"要整站名Poster可以用地鐵最有特色嘅書法字嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kJ2TNJ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkJ2TNJ4.jpg&h=ebb412a1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}